{"tid":1768332,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"官斥警未交匿名理據","createTime":"2019-12-04T03:52:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T05:47:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9df15102a8e4e69cc3de8bb2451461dd9afd4780","tid":1768332,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T03:52:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191204/EDDDWY7FLLEBKX7WYNKJ3TJW44/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191204%2FEDDDWY7FLLEBKX7WYNKJ3TJW44%2F&d=sHvBfS5bCv0nfD6zjI7mDR5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=edc5d59e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191204%2FEDDDWY7FLLEBKX7WYNKJ3TJW44%2F&h=448d8b6f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191204/EDDDWY7FLLEBKX7WYNKJ3TJW44/</a><br />\n<br />\n官斥警未交匿名理據<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191204/large/1575390138_f797.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191204%2Flarge%2F1575390138_f797.jpg&h=85fe391b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被控襲警的謝煒洛10月首次提堂後，由其他人掩護離開法庭。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】律政司近月起訴示威者襲警或阻差辦公罪行時，屢將牽涉的警務人員姓名以編號或英文字母取代，待遇與風化案事主相同。一名被控襲警的中大學生，早前提堂時明言反對警員匿名；事隔近兩個月，控方昨天仍未能提供書面法律理據。警方即席草擬簡單理據，並申請再押後，遭裁判官質疑：「我唔明白點解要咁耐囉！我真係唔明。」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：大膽敢言 多次唱淡大市<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n即場草擬指憂被起底<br />\n<br />\n男被告謝煒洛（21歲）被控襲警及管有攻擊性武器罪，控罪指他於今年10月20日在旺角亞皆老街與旺角道之間的塘尾道襲擊警長X並管有兩塊磚頭。案件於10月22日首次提訊，並押後昨天再訊。<br />\n<br />\n辯方昨指，仍未收到控方有關匿名處理涉案警察的理據。控方回應稱需作整體考慮，因有關安排將「一次過」適用於「全香港九龍新界」的案件，而非獨立針對某個警務人員，故需更多時間預備。<br />\n<br />\n署理主任裁判官嚴舜儀直指，控方申請「相信係有啲原因啦」，但謂「我都想知」，並稱控方只需將有關原因告知辯方，惟不應再押後。<br />\n<br />\n控方遂讀出警方即場草擬的理據，聲稱網上有針對警員的起底，擔心個人資料被公開會危及人身安全，故申請匿名。案件最終押後至明年2月7日再訊。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：KCCC2598/19"},{"pid":"4322cef9632e841e64cb00242807447b0109c937","tid":1768332,"uid":42350,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T03:57:22.000Z","msg":"無名無姓全部告唔入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab34bdb7d8e2ef86b99764d9ccdd2f0933b525d4","tid":1768332,"uid":113902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T04:00:13.000Z","msg":"到時隻狗上庭作證洗唔洗強姦案咁開一間房 視像作供<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"122d045e789b2b2724cd001dd66e653112ec0c16","tid":1768332,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T04:06:34.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">日程表</span></span></strong><br />\n－－－－－－<strong><em>和理非合法活動集合</em></strong>－－－－－－</div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">星期五 12 &middot; 6 </span><br />\n「吸吸可危」抵禦催淚彈集會</strong></span><br />\n- 19:00 愛丁堡廣場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1766230/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1766230/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">星期六 12 &middot; 7</span><br />\n聲援被無理禁錮印尼手足</strong></span><br />\n- 15:00 愛丁堡廣場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1767815/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1767815/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">星期日 12 &middot; 8</span><br />\n國際人權日遊行</strong></span><br />\n- 15:00 維園＞遮打道<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1765090/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1765090/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n詳情參閱：<a href=\"https://hkrev.info/march.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkrev.info%2Fmarch.php&d=sHvBfS5bCv0nfD6zjI7mDR5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=80399920\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkrev.info/march.php</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span s